import { Button as MuiButton, Grid } from '@mui/material'
import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core'
import User from '../../../../public/assets/user.svg'
import Help from '../../../../public/assets/help.svg'
import Notification from '../../../../public/assets/notification.svg'

import Icon from '../../Atoms/Icon/Icon'
import TypographyComponent from '../../Atoms/Typography/TypographyComponent'
import Dossier from '../../../../public/assets/dossier-header.svg'
import Avatar from '../../Atoms/Avatar/Avatar'

export type headerProps = {}

export const Header = (props: headerProps) => {
  const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
    dossierIcon: {
      paddingLeft: 'auto',
      paddingUp: 'auto',
      width: '18px',
      height: '18px',
      paddingTop:'10px'
    },
    icon: {
      paddingLeft: '8px',
      paddingTop:'10px'

    },
    avatar:{
    height:'36px',
    width:'36px',
    paddingTop:'3px'
    },
    text: {
      fontSize: '18px',
      lineHeight: '20px',
      width: '76px',
      height: '20px',
      fontFamily: 'Poppins',
      fontWeight: 500,
      paddingTop:'10px'
    },
  }))
  const classes = useStyles()

  return (
    <Grid
      container
      direction="row"
      spacing={1}
      style={{
        border: '1px solid #D4D2D9',
        width:'1336px',
        height:'64px',
        

      }}
    >
      <Grid item>
        <Icon imageSrc={Dossier} classname={classes.dossierIcon}></Icon>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item md={10} sm={4} style={{}}>
        <TypographyComponent
          variant="body1"
          text="DOSSIER"
          color="#4C2CD9"
          classname={classes.text}
        ></TypographyComponent>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item >
        <Icon imageSrc={Help} classname={classes.icon}></Icon>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item >
        <Icon imageSrc={Notification} classname={classes.icon}></Icon>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item >
        <Avatar variant={'circular'} src={User} classname={classes.avatar}></Avatar>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  )
}
